data.description: Welcome to this beautifully updated home nestled in the gated community of Tuscany Pointe minutes from Founders Square & zoned for Schools with 'A' Rating! This 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom concrete block residence is in prime location of the neighborhood featuring no backyard neighbors! As you approach, your eyes are drawn to the extended brick paver driveway & lush landscaping. Entering the foyer you notice freshly painted interior & new luxury vinyl plank floors that extend throughout the entire home. The trendy & newly updated kitchen features: fresh white with gray veined quartz countertops, crisp white subway tile backsplash, stainless steel undermount sink & kitchen faucet with touch feature. Enjoy cooking for family & friends in your open concept living area, complete with crown molding detail. Just off the kitchen is your spacious primary bedroom with two walk-in closets & en-suite bathroom featuring double sinks, granite countertops, ample storage space, glass walk-in shower & water closet. Breathe in the fresh air while relaxing on your screened in lanai featuring two fans, while overlooking your private backyard oasis. Schedule your showing of this stunning home today!
